    • Method Detail

      • configure

        public void configure(InRange range)

        Tells this generator to produce values within a specified minimum and/or maximum, inclusive, with uniform distribution, down to the nanosecond.

        If an endpoint of the range is not specified, the generator will use dates with values of either OffsetDateTime.MIN or OffsetDateTime.MAX as appropriate.

        InRange.format() describes how the generator is to interpret the range's endpoints.

        Parameters:
        range - annotation that gives the range's constraints
